#Make new variable: Set "Good" and "Bad" Loans, all else "blank" to be removed later
df <-
  loans50k %>%
  mutate(payment_status = case_when(
    status == "Fully Paid" ~ "Good", 
    status == "Charged Off" ~ "Bad",
    TRUE ~ ""
  ))
#change the empty string cells to NAs
df[df==""]<-NA
